data.description: This stunning custom built home features exquisite designer touches,neutral coloring, and is move-in ready!  Located within walking distance of the new municipal building/park and a conveniently located near the elementary school. This immaculate home has upgraded lighting and faucets thoughout. The downstairs features a generous living space, powder room, built in lockers for storage in the mudroom, and an eat-in kitchen with gorgeous granite Kitchen counter tops and island.  Upstairs boasts all four bedrooms,two bathrooms, laundry room and storage galore! while Master Suite features double doors, his & her vanities and a large walk- in closet.  You will love the large basement, 2 car garage, inviting front porch, the backyard with a playset. Seller is an Ohio licensed R.E agent
